  "title": "Static friction - effect of changing force on box",
  "content": {
    "prompt": "<div><div class=\"stimulus_reference\"><div class=\"passage\"><div class=\"prose style:1\"><div class=\"standalone_image\"><img alt=\"Two figures are shown, labeled Figure 1 and Figure 2. In each figure, a box is placed on a rough horizontal surface. In Figure 1, a rightward pointing arrow labeled F is drawn from the right side of the box. In Figure 2, a rightward pointing arrow labeled with the fraction F over 2 is drawn from the right side of the box.\" src=\"/images/70d1a6a0819b97a9e7a4d86bcb8552ba.svg\"></div></div></div></div></div><p class=\"stem_paragraph\">In Figure <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"1\"><math alttext=\"1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>1</mn></math></span></span>, a force of magnitude <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"F\"><math alttext=\"F\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi>F</mi></math></span></span> is exerted horizontally on a box resting on a rough, horizontal surface. A force exerted horizontally with a magnitude greater than <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"F\"><math alttext=\"F\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi>F</mi></math></span></span> will cause the box to slide. In Figure <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"2\"><math alttext=\"2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>2</mn></math></span></span>, the force <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"F\"><math alttext=\"F\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi>F</mi></math></span></span> is removed and a force of magnitude <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"the fraction F over 2\"><math alttext=\"the fraction F over 2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mfrac><mi>F</mi><mn>2</mn></mfrac></math></span></span> is then exerted on the same box. Which of the following statements about the box in Figure <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"2\"><math alttext=\"2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>2</mn></math></span></span> must be true?</p>\n",
    "answer": "i1",
    "choices": [
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">The force of static friction on the box will be equal to <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"the fraction F over 2\"><math alttext=\"the fraction F over 2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mfrac><mi>F</mi><mn>2</mn></mfrac></math></span></span>.</p>",
        "value": "i1"
      },
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">The force of static friction on the box will be equal to <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"F\"><math alttext=\"F\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi>F</mi></math></span></span>.</p>",
        "value": "i2"
      },
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">The box will begin sliding to the left.</p>",
        "value": "i3"
      },
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">The box will begin sliding to the right.</p>",
        "value": "i4"
      }
    ]
  },
